:touch
Phoebe: Yes?

Cleatle: Oh, nothing.
#end
:touch
Phoebe: Yes?

Cleatle: Would you mind giving me Mr.
Shapiro's phone number?

Phoebe: That's a confidential number.

Cleatle: So?

Phoebe: Good point... he hasn't given me
any raises lately. And he's been having
me do too much stapling. I don't like
stapling.

Cleatle: Stapling is bad! Mr. Shapiro
cares not for your rights as an employee!

Phoebe: I will rebel! (suddenly calm)
Here's his number.

Cleatle: Thanks.

(Phoebe hands Cleatle a slip of paper.)
#give ammo 1
#zap touch
#end
:touch
Cleatle: I have nothing more to say.
